## Installation

```bash
./install_hardware_b450-i-aorus-pro-wifi.sh | tee install_hardware.log
./install.sh 2>&1 | tee install.log
./post_install.sh your-email@example.com | tee post_install.log

./scripts/check.sh
```

Update manually installed packages

```bash
./scripts/update.sh
```
